items.shortDescription: The EPIK Learning Intel Quad Core 7" Kids' Tablet brings your child a compact, ultra-portable entertainment device that will let them read email, surf the Internet, read ebooks, view photos, play games, listen to music and watch video files. The tablets are based on a smaller operating system, which allows you to purchase and download additional applications from supported stores for your child to enjoy. This device is a truly smooth all-in-one solution for education and fun. It is preloaded with award-winning mobile apps for children and adults, such as Looney Tunes Phonics, SmartRunner Series, ClickN Spell, Google Play and much more. The 16GB tablet provides plenty of storage for all of the entertaining and learning apps your child will want to use. They come in a bright arrangement of colors, allowing you to choose your little one's favorite look. The system offers up to five hours at a time on a full charge, giving lots of time for play. It comes with a battery, gel case and AC adapter, so your child can start using it right away.
